snippet.title: Svea Rike
snippet.description:
Svea rike was developed by Korkeken Interactive Studio AB, Target Games Interactive AB and published by Levande böcker i norden AB in 1997 for Windows, Windows 3.x and Machintosh. 

Svea Rike is a real-time strategy game based on the history of Sweden. The game take place between year 1523 until 1818, and the goal is to end up as king over Sweden. The player has to carefully manage his resource and invest wisely in trade, improvements and politics.

I am running this in VMware using a Windows 2000-image.
